  "remarks": "LLC Yadran-Group is a Russian conglomerate established in Tatarstan and mainly active in the oil sector, including in the extraction, processing and sale of oil and oil products. The oil sector is a sector providing substantial revenue to the Russian Government. Therefore, LLC Yadran-Group is involved in an economic sector providing a substantial source of revenue to the Government of the Russian Federation, which is responsible for the annexation of Crimea and the destabilisation of Ukraine.",
